def make_report(y_pred , y_true):
    print ("")
    print ("Classification Report: ")
    print (classification_report(y_true, y_pred))
    cm = confusion_matrix(y_true, y_pred)
    fig, ax = plot_confusion_matrix(conf_mat=cm)
    plt.show()

def undersampleing(v = 1):
    new_y_train.hist()
    plt.title('before NearMiss-{}'.format(v))
    plt.show()

    undersample = NearMiss(version=v, n_neighbors=3)
    X_train_resample, y_train_resample = undersample.fit_resample(X_train, new_y_train)

    y_train_resample.hist()
    plt.title('after NearMiss-{}'.format(v))
    plt.show()

    clf = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(),
                        LogisticRegression())
    clf.fit(X_train_resample, y_train_resample)
    pred = clf.predict(X_test)
    make_report(pred, new_y_test)

q6: Forward Selection¶

In [107]:
%%time
def forward_selection(X, y, model, score):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.20, random_state=42)
    outer_max ={'adjusted_R2': -2, 'feature_set': []}
    fixed = []
    for j in range(len(X.columns)):
        inner_max = {'AUC': -2, 'feature': 0, 'adjusted_R2': -2}
        for i in X.columns:
            if i in fixed:
                continue
            current_features = fixed+[i]
            model.fit(X_train[current_features], y_train)
            pred = model.predict_proba(X_train[current_features])
            s = score(label_binarize(y_train, classes=[0, 1, 2, 3]), pred, multi_class="ovo", average="weighted")
            if s > inner_max['AUC']:
                inner_max['AUC'] = s
                inner_max['feature'] = i
                inner_max['adjusted_R2'] = 1 - (1-model.score(X_test[current_features], y_test))*(len(y_test)-1)/(len(y_test)-X_test[current_features].shape[1]-1)
        if inner_max['feature'] != 0:
            fixed = fixed+[inner_max['feature']]
            if outer_max['adjusted_R2'] < inner_max['adjusted_R2']:
                outer_max['adjusted_R2'] = inner_max['adjusted_R2']
                outer_max['feature_set'] = fixed
        else:
            return outer_max['feature_set']
    return outer_max['feature_set']
        


clf = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(), LogisticRegression())    
forward_selection_features = forward_selection(X = X_train, y = y_train, model = clf, score = roc_auc_score)
print(len(forward_selection_features), forward_selection_features)

%%time
def backward_selection(X, y, model, score):
    X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.20, random_state=42)
    outer_max ={'adjusted_R2': -2, 'feature_set': []}
    fixed = list(X_train.columns)
    for j in range(len(X.columns)-1):
        inner_max = {'AUC': -2, 'feature': 0, 'adjusted_R2': -2}
        for i in X.columns:
            if i not in fixed:
                continue
            current_features = [f for f in fixed if f != i]
            model.fit(X_train[current_features], y_train)
            pred = model.predict_proba(X_train[current_features])
            s = score(label_binarize(y_train, classes=[0, 1, 2, 3]), pred, multi_class="ovo", average="weighted")
            if s > inner_max['AUC']:
                inner_max['AUC'] = s
                inner_max['feature'] = i
                inner_max['adjusted_R2'] = 1 - (1-model.score(X_test[current_features], y_test))*(len(y_test)-1)/(len(y_test)-X_test[current_features].shape[1]-1)
        if inner_max['feature'] != 0:
            fixed = [f for f in fixed if f != inner_max['feature']]
            if outer_max['adjusted_R2'] < inner_max['adjusted_R2']:
                outer_max['adjusted_R2'] = inner_max['adjusted_R2']
                outer_max['feature_set'] = fixed
        else:
            return outer_max['feature_set']
    return outer_max['feature_set']
        

clf = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(), LogisticRegression())    
backward_selection_features = backward_selection(X = X_train, y = y_train, model = clf, score = roc_auc_score)
print(len(backward_selection_features), backward_selection_features)

In [132]:
scoring={'F1 weighted': 'f1_weighted', 'Accuracy': 'accuracy', 'Precision weighted': 'precision_weighted', 'Recall weighted': 'recall_weighted',
        'F1 macro': 'f1_macro', 'Precision macro': 'precision_macro', 'Recall macro': 'recall_macro'}
def prep_result(temp, cv = 5):
    n_temp = {}
    n_temp['cv'] = cv
    for key, value in temp.items():
        if 'time' in key:
            n_temp['{}_mean'.format(key)] = value.mean()
            n_temp['{}_variance'.format(key)] = value.var()
            continue
        n_temp['{}_mean'.format(key.split('_')[1])] = value.mean()
        n_temp['{}_variance'.format(key.split('_')[1])] = value.var()
    return n_temp

clf = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(),
                    LogisticRegression())

temp1 = cross_validate(clf, data.drop('price_range', axis=1), data['price_range'], cv=5, scoring=scoring)
temp1 = prep_result(temp1, cv = 5)
temp2 = cross_validate(clf, data.drop('price_range', axis=1), data['price_range'], cv=10, scoring=scoring)
temp2 = prep_result(temp2, cv = 10)

r = pd.DataFrame([temp1, temp2])
display(r)
r.to_csv(path+'cv_results.csv', index = False)
